This a playground for extensions to project lombok (https://github.com/rzwitserloot/lombok)

The current extensions are:

  - @AutoGenMethodStub
  - @Builder and @BuilderExtension
  - @FluentSetter
  - @ListenerSupport
  - @WriteLock, @ReadLock, @Await, @Signal, @AwaitBeforeAndSignalAfter
  - @Singleton
  - @SwingInvokeLater and @SwingInvokeAndWait
  - Interfaces lombok.Application and lombok.JVMAgent (Entrypoint Generation)
  - With.with(object, expr1, expr2, ...)

If you like to try it out, fetch a copy from here:
http://cloud.github.com/downloads/peichhorn/lombok-pg/lombok-pg-0.10.0-BETA2-HEAD.jar (lombok 0.10.0 BETA2 + lombok-pg)